===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|gl|/laˈpaɾ/}}

===Verb===
{{gl-verb|lap|ar}}

# to [[lick]], to [[lap]]
# to [[quaff]], to [[swig]]
# to [[slurp]]; to [[eat]] disorderly or compulsively
